description: Try our easy to follow Bubba's Chicken, Apple And Carrot Mash recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Baby food,Seafood free,Low salt,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Low sugar,Sesame free,High protein,Wheat free,Apple,Rice,Mince,Chicken,Dairy free
name: Bubba's Chicken, Apple And Carrot Mash Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Combine chicken mince, apple, carrot, dill, garlic and egg in a medium bowl. Using your hands form into 10 patties.
Heat oil in a large frying pan over medium heat. Cook patties for 4 minutes on each side or until cooked through.
Add rice and some water. Allow to cool before puréeing to desired consistency for baby’s developmental age and serving. Serves 10 baby portions
